    <note>Lu(1) Bing [1273] His father, Ge [3625], passed the child prodigy exam. Ge was originally a Huzhou, Dexing resident, who lived in Suzhou, Wuxian for fifteen years after he retired from the civil  service. When he died at the age of 82, he was buried in Wuxian, which became the family's permanent address. Zhiyuan's [1267] and Fayuan's [1270] father. Daoyuan [7300] and Zongyuan [1276] have the same generational names as his sons. XCB, 266.3a, 273.16b, 99.1b, 20a, 304.15b, 478.10b; XCBSB, 4.19a (n.); SS, 331.27a-27b; Wujun zhi, 25.11b; YLDD, 2367.11b, 12507.12a; Zhejiang TZ, 123.25b. CBD, 5, 4019.</note>
